oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Louisiana Folk Life Festival (2004)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Festivals; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and green on white) announcing the Louisiana Folklife Festival featuring Irma Thomas, Victoria Williams, Ingrid Lucia, Vickie Baker and Charmaine Neville in downtown Monroe, Louisiana on September 11 and 12. Poster features a metal photoplate of a diver.
